history.proof: intros l i e' H. induction l as [|e es IH]. - simpl in H. discriminate. - simpl in H. destruct (eIndex e =? i) eqn:Heq. ++ inversion H; subst. apply Nat.eqb_eq in Heq. auto. ++ destruct (eIndex e <? i) eqn:Heqlt. ** discriminate. ** apply IH in H. auto.
